history.content: Please waitlist yourself.  Those who have a reserved seat will be manually enrolled from the waitlist into the class.

children.subject:
You only need to add yourself to the lecture waitlist, but in doing that you should be prompted to select which lab/discussion sections you'd like. If and when you have a seat in the lecture, you would also get into the lab/discussion sections you selected. 

It's helpful to choose secondary sections that will likely have available seats.  The only way our system will let you into the class is if you have a seat in all three sections.  Please feel free to email me directly for any follow up questions.
